           Another example that mainstream hardcore in Germany is booming. 
           Another CD has come out on More Music once more. Perhaps less 
           tracks than his german ''brother'', but still a very nice 
           compilation for the hardcore heads out there. Shame that some
           tracks are on the other compilation as well

           Ow, too bad the Germans have a hard time with artist names and 
           track titles. I hope I sort things out for the most part.
